high_descs: Walk to the sofa in front of you.
Pick up the egg from the couch.
Turn right and head towards the table, then hang a right and go to the microwave in the left corner of the room.
Put the egg into the microwave.
Turn around and go to the diningtable to your left.
Pick up the egg from the pan on the table.
Turn right and go back to the microwave to your left.
Put the egg into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put two Egg into the Microwave

high_descs: Walk straight and turn left to reach the sofa.
Take the egg from the couch.
Turn right and walk straight and turn right and reach the left side rack in which the microwave is placed.
Open the microwave and place the egg inside the microwave and close it.
Turn back and again turn right to reach the diningtable.
Take the egg from the frying pan.
Turn right and walk towards the microwave on the left side in which microwave oven is placed.
Open the microwave and place the egg inside the microwave and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put the eggs inside the microwave

high_descs: Stand up turn around move towards the sofa.
Take the egg from the sofa.
Turn around move towards the microwave.
Keep the egg inside the microwave.
Turn around move towards the dining table.
Take the egg from the dining table.
Turn around move towards the microwave.
Keep the egg inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Take the eggs from the sofa and dining table, keep it inside the microwave.
